<p align="center" style="text-align:center; text-indent:.25in"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:white">Code 99213 (Established) or 99203 (New) - you will sometimes have a level 3 visit when addressing only one problem or providing no prescriptions</span></span></span></b></span></span></span></p>
